data.description: Welcome to your coastal retreat! This charming 1955 beach cottage is a timeless sanctuary that invites you to unwind and embrace the coastal lifestyle. With breathtaking ocean views, this property offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern comfort. The kitchen boasts modern amenities while retaining its classic appeal. There is also a mother-in-law suite ideal for long-term guests. This property features unobstructed ocean views, covered front deck for outdoor living, gas fireplace for those chilly evenings, and proximity to local amenities and attractions.Whether you're seeking a permanent residence, a vacation home, or an investment property, this beach cottage is a rare find.
